Package: DStressR
Title: Differential Stress-Response Modeling for Chemical Genomics Screens
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Christian L.", family = "Müller", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ch.mueller@lmu.de")
  )
Author: Christian L. Müller
Maintainer: Christian L. Müller <ch.mueller@lmu.de>
Description: Companion workflow to DGrowthR for model-based differential
    promoter activity analysis in high-throughput chemical genomics screens.
    DStressR models growth-adjusted luminescence, compound-wide effects,
    promoter-specific stress responses, empirical-Bayes promoter variance
    moderation, and technical covariates.
URL: https://muellsen.github.io/DStressR/, https://github.com/muellsen/DStressR/
BugReports: https://github.com/muellsen/DStressR/issues
